---
import Base from "../layouts/Base.astro";
---

<Base
  title="About"
  description="Simply Ltd — the story of how a single falafel truck on Paddington Basin became a fleet."
>
  <article class="about">
    {/* Hero ----------------------------------------------------------------- */}
    <section class="about-hero" aria-labelledby="about-hero-heading">
      <div class="about-hero__inner">
        <p class="t-caption about-hero__kicker">About Simply Ltd</p>
        <h1 id="about-hero-heading" class="t-display about-hero__heading">
          A single falafel truck. <br />Now a fleet on the canal.
        </h1>
        <p class="t-editorial t-editorial--italic about-hero__dek">
          We've been on Paddington Basin since 2019. What started with one wrap has grown into three
          trucks, multiple concepts, and a queue that doesn't stop. The standards haven't moved.
        </p>
      </div>
    </section>

    {/* Origin story --------------------------------------------------------- */}
    <section class="origin" aria-labelledby="origin-heading">
      <div class="origin__inner">
        <header class="origin__header">
          <p class="t-caption">The story</p>
          <h2 id="origin-heading" class="t-display origin__heading">How it grew.</h2>
        </header>

        <div class="t-prose origin__prose">
          <p>
            Our journey began in 2019 with a single food truck: <strong>Simply Falafel</strong>.
            Built from a love of Levantine street food and a stubborn belief that quality matters,
            it found its audience quickly. The queue grew before the marketing did.
          </p>

          <p>
            By 2021 the response had outgrown the menu. We added <strong>Simply Shawarma</strong>,
            bringing bold traditional shawarma flavours to the canal. The same team, the same
            standards, a different cuisine. Two queues on Merchant Square.
          </p>

          <p>
            In 2023 we combined the best of both into <strong>Simply Lebanese</strong> for catered
            events — a complete Levantine offering for tables that wanted the whole spread. It runs
            off-rota now, primarily for catering, but it's still the most-requested package we do.
          </p>

          <p>
            Then came the burger. <strong>Simply Burgers</strong> launched because people kept
            asking us for one. Smash burgers, lacy crispy edges, melted American, soft brioche,
            dialled-in sauce. It sits on Canal Side Walk, 250 metres east of the other trucks.
          </p>

          <p>
            We're now three operating trucks across two pitches on Paddington Basin. The standards
            are the same on every menu: fresh, on the truck, every day.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    {/* Values --------------------------------------------------------------- */}
    <section class="values" aria-labelledby="values-heading">
      <div class="values__inner">
        <header class="values__header">
          <p class="t-caption">What we believe</p>
          <h2 id="values-heading" class="t-display values__heading">Three things, on every menu.</h2>
        </header>

        <ol role="list" class="values__list">
          <li class="value">
            <p class="t-display value__numeral" aria-hidden="true">01</p>
            <h3 class="t-display value__title">Quality</h3>
            <p class="t-body value__body">
              Real ingredients, properly handled. Marinades go in early. Doughs proved long. Sauces
              from scratch.
            </p>
          </li>
          <li class="value">
            <p class="t-display value__numeral" aria-hidden="true">02</p>
            <h3 class="t-display value__title">Simplicity</h3>
            <p class="t-body value__body">
              Small menus, done well. We'd rather make one wrap brilliantly than ten things
              passably.
            </p>
          </li>
          <li class="value">
            <p class="t-display value__numeral" aria-hidden="true">03</p>
            <h3 class="t-display value__title">Consistency</h3>
            <p class="t-body value__body">
              Monday's burger is Friday's burger. Trip after trip, that's the only way the queue
              stays.
            </p>
          </li>
        </ol>
      </div>
    </section>

    {/* Fleet links ---------------------------------------------------------- */}
    <section class="fleet" aria-labelledby="fleet-heading">
      <div class="fleet__inner">
        <header class="fleet__header">
          <p class="t-caption">Three concepts, one parent</p>
          <h2 id="fleet-heading" class="t-display fleet__heading">Meet the fleet.</h2>
        </header>

        <ul role="list" class="fleet__grid">
          <li data-brand="falafel" class="fleet__item">
            <a href="/falafel/" class="fleet__link">
              <p class="t-caption">Simply</p>
              <h3 class="t-display fleet__wordmark">Falafel</h3>
              <p class="t-editorial t-editorial--italic fleet__dek">Vegan Levantine. Where it all started.</p>
              <span class="fleet__arrow" aria-hidden="true">Visit →</span>
            </a>
          </li>
          <li data-brand="shawarma" class="fleet__item">
            <a href="/shawarma/" class="fleet__link">
              <p class="t-caption">Simply</p>
              <h3 class="t-display fleet__wordmark">Shawarma</h3>
              <p class="t-editorial t-editorial--italic fleet__dek">Bold, traditional, late-night fast.</p>
              <span class="fleet__arrow" aria-hidden="true">Visit →</span>
            </a>
          </li>
          <li data-brand="burgers" class="fleet__item">
            <a href="/burgers/" class="fleet__link">
              <p class="t-caption">Simply</p>
              <h3 class="t-display fleet__wordmark">Burgers</h3>
              <p class="t-editorial t-editorial--italic fleet__dek">Smash burgers, no compromise.</p>
              <span class="fleet__arrow" aria-hidden="true">Visit →</span>
            </a>
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </section>

    {/* CTA ------------------------------------------------------------------ */}
    <section class="about-cta" aria-labelledby="about-cta-heading">
      <div class="about-cta__inner">
        <h2 id="about-cta-heading" class="t-display about-cta__heading">
          Work with us.
        </h2>
        <p class="t-editorial t-editorial--italic about-cta__dek">
          Catering enquiries, franchising opportunities, or just say hello.
        </p>
        <div class="about-cta__links">
          <a href="/catering/" class="about-cta__link about-cta__link--primary">
            Catering enquiries
            <span aria-hidden="true">→</span>
          </a>
          <a href="/franchising/" class="about-cta__link about-cta__link--secondary">
            Franchising
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
  </article>
</Base>

<style>
  /* Hero */
  .about-hero {
    padding: var(--sp-7) var(--page-gutter) var(--sp-6);
    background: var(--color-cream);
  }
  .about-hero__inner {
    max-width: var(--page-max);
    margin: 0 auto;
  }
  .about-hero__kicker {
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
    margin-bottom: var(--sp-3);
  }
  .about-hero__heading {
    font-size: clamp(var(--fs-700), 9vw, var(--fs-800));
    line-height: 0.92;
    letter-spacing: var(--ls-display-tight);
  }
  .about-hero__dek {
    margin-top: var(--sp-4);
    font-size: var(--fs-400);
    max-width: 56ch;
    color: color-mix(in srgb, var(--color-ink) 80%, transparent);
  }

  /* Origin */
  .origin {
    padding: var(--sp-7) var(--page-gutter);
    background: var(--color-cream);
    border-top: 1px solid var(--color-line);
  }
  .origin__inner {
    max-width: var(--page-max);
    margin: 0 auto;
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    gap: var(--sp-5);
  }
  @media (min-width: 900px) {
    .origin__inner {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr 2fr;
      gap: var(--sp-7);
    }
  }
  .origin__heading {
    font-size: clamp(var(--fs-600), 6vw, var(--fs-700));
    line-height: 1;
  }
  .origin__prose {
    max-width: var(--measure-prose);
  }
  .origin__prose strong {
    font-weight: var(--fw-strong);
  }

  /* Values */
  .values {
    padding: var(--sp-7) var(--page-gutter);
    background: var(--color-paper);
    border-top: 1px solid var(--color-line);
  }
  .values__inner {
    max-width: var(--page-max);
    margin: 0 auto;
  }
  .values__header {
    margin-bottom: var(--sp-5);
  }
  .values__heading {
    font-size: clamp(var(--fs-600), 6vw, var(--fs-700));
    line-height: 1;
    margin-top: var(--sp-2);
  }
  .values__list {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    gap: var(--sp-4);
  }
  @media (min-width: 720px) {
    .values__list {
      grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
    }
  }
  .value {
    padding: var(--sp-4);
    background: var(--color-cream);
    border-radius: var(--r-md);
  }
  .value__numeral {
    font-size: var(--fs-700);
    line-height: 1;
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
  }
  .value__title {
    font-size: var(--fs-500);
    margin-top: var(--sp-2);
    line-height: 1;
  }
  .value__body {
    margin-top: var(--sp-2);
    font-size: var(--fs-300);
    line-height: var(--lh-relaxed);
  }

  /* Fleet (re-uses cross-links pattern from brand pages) */
  .fleet {
    padding: var(--sp-7) var(--page-gutter);
    background: var(--color-cream);
    border-top: 1px solid var(--color-line);
  }
  .fleet__inner {
    max-width: var(--page-max);
    margin: 0 auto;
  }
  .fleet__header {
    margin-bottom: var(--sp-5);
  }
  .fleet__heading {
    font-size: clamp(var(--fs-600), 6vw, var(--fs-700));
    line-height: 1;
    margin-top: var(--sp-2);
  }
  .fleet__grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    gap: var(--sp-3);
  }
  @media (min-width: 720px) {
    .fleet__grid {
      grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
    }
  }
  .fleet__item {
    background: var(--color-accent);
    color: var(--color-accent-contrast);
    border-radius: var(--r-lg);
    overflow: hidden;
    transition: transform var(--dur-base) var(--ease-out);
  }
  .fleet__item:has(.fleet__link:hover),
  .fleet__item:has(.fleet__link:focus-visible) {
    transform: translateY(-3px);
  }
  .fleet__link {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: var(--sp-2);
    padding: var(--sp-5);
    text-decoration: none;
    color: inherit;
    min-height: 240px;
  }
  .fleet__link :focus-visible {
    outline: 2px solid currentColor;
    outline-offset: 3px;
  }
  .fleet__wordmark {
    font-size: var(--fs-700);
    line-height: 0.92;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: var(--ls-display-tight);
  }
  .fleet__dek {
    font-size: var(--fs-300);
    color: var(--color-accent-contrast);
    margin-top: var(--sp-1);
  }
  .fleet__arrow {
    margin-top: auto;
    font-family: var(--ff-body-stack);
    font-weight: var(--fw-strong);
    font-size: var(--fs-200);
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: var(--ls-caption);
    padding-top: var(--sp-3);
  }

  /* About CTA (re-uses locations bottom-cta pattern) */
  .about-cta {
    background: var(--color-ink);
    color: var(--color-cream);
    padding: var(--sp-7) var(--page-gutter);
  }
  .about-cta__inner {
    max-width: var(--page-max);
    margin: 0 auto;
    text-align: center;
  }
  .about-cta__heading {
    font-size: clamp(var(--fs-600), 5vw, var(--fs-700));
    line-height: 1;
  }
  .about-cta__dek {
    margin-top: var(--sp-3);
    font-size: var(--fs-400);
    color: color-mix(in srgb, var(--color-cream) 80%, transparent);
  }
  .about-cta__links {
    margin-top: var(--sp-5);
    display: flex;
    justify-content: center;
    gap: var(--sp-3);
    flex-wrap: wrap;
  }
  .about-cta__link {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: var(--sp-2);
    padding: var(--sp-3) var(--sp-4);
    font-family: var(--ff-body-stack);
    font-weight: var(--fw-strong);
    font-size: var(--fs-200);
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: var(--ls-caption);
    text-decoration: none;
    border-radius: var(--r-pill);
    transition: transform var(--dur-fast) var(--ease-out);
  }
  .about-cta__link--primary {
    background: var(--color-cream);
    color: var(--color-ink);
  }
  .about-cta__link--secondary {
    background: transparent;
    color: var(--color-cream);
    border: 1.5px solid var(--color-cream);
  }
  .about-cta__link:hover,
  .about-cta__link:focus-visible {
    transform: translateY(-1px);
  }
  .about-cta :focus-visible {
    outline: 2px solid var(--color-cream);
    outline-offset: 3px;
  }
</style>
